OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F413A1774458667
OL,3,CWildlife charity 'heartbroken' at
OL,4,Chaving to euthanise wolf pack
OL,6,FA wildlife charity in Kent has
OL,7,Fconfirmed that it was left "with no
OL,8,Fchoice" but to put its pack of wolves
OL,9,Fto sleep.
OL,11,FStaff at the Wildwood Trust near
OL,12,FCanterbury say they are "deeply
OL,13,Fsaddened at the difficult decision"
OL,14,Fafter three of the five wolves were
OL,15,Fseriously injured.
OL,17,FThe charity said the pack's dynamics
OL,18,Fbroke down, which created an
OL,19,Fincreasing risk to the animals' safety
OL,20,Fand quality of life.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/5
