PN,41302
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F413A1774458667
OL,3,CWildlife charity 'heartbroken' at
OL,4,Chaving to euthanise wolf pack
OL,6,FPaul Whitfield, Wildwood Trust's
OL,7,FDirector General, says it is an
OL,8,Fincredibly difficult time for everyone
OL,9,Fat Wildwood: "Our keepers care hugely
OL,10,Fabout these animals and did everything
OL,11,Fthey could to find a way forward.
OL,13,F"Wolves are highly social animals that
OL,14,Flive within complex family structures,
OL,15,Fand when those dynamics break down,
OL,16,Fconflict and rejection can increase.
OL,17,FIn this case, it led to ongoing
OL,18,Fwelfare concerns and an unacceptable
OL,19,Frisk of serious injury.
OL,26,@qD@NOU
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/5
