PN,41303
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F413A1774458667
OL,3,CWildlife charity 'heartbroken' at
OL,4,Chaving to euthanise wolf pack
OL,6,F"Euthanasia is never taken lightly,
OL,7,Fbut in responsible animal care it can
OL,8,Fsometimes be the most humane option
OL,9,Fwhen welfare can no longer be
OL,10,Fmaintained.
OL,12,F"This decision was an absolute last
OL,13,Fresort, with the animals' welfare as
OL,14,Four priority. It's incredibly
OL,15,Fdifficult, but it was ultimately the
OL,16,Fright thing to do to prevent further
OL,17,Fsuffering."
OL,26,@nD@AOUyD@KO]
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/5
