PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F413A1774458667
OL,3,CWildlife charity 'heartbroken' at
OL,4,Chaving to euthanise wolf pack
OL,6,FThe charity said it brought together
OL,7,Fexperienced keepers and vets to try
OL,8,Fand stabilise the group but that it
OL,9,Fwas clear they were no longer able to
OL,10,Flive together as a stable pack.
OL,12,FThe situation had been monitored
OL,13,Fclosely over time, with regular
OL,14,Fassessment by experienced keepers and
OL,15,Fveterinary professionals. As the
OL,16,Fanimals' quality of life significantly
OL,17,Fdeteriorated and could not be improved
OL,18,Fto an acceptable level, the decision
OL,19,Fwas made to act in their best
OL,20,Finterests.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G4/5
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
